{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01XCNraveesKuyJjcr2waQrk","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the problems:\n\n1. **`/app` vhost:**\n   - `ops-user` has full configure/write/read permissions on `/app` — this should be removed (ops-user should only have access to /ops)\n   - `app-user` has configure=\"\" (empty), write=\".*\", read=\".*\" — the configure permission is broken/empty. It needs to be `.*`\n\n2. **`/ops` vhost:**\n   - `ops-user` has NO permissions listed on `/ops` — this needs to be added with full configure/write/read\n   - `app-user` has no permissions on `/ops` — this is correct, no action needed\n   \nSo I need to revoke `ops-user`'s access to `/app`, fix `app-user`'s configure permission there, and grant `ops-user` full permissions on `/ops`. Let me also look at how the app-client and ops-client deployments are connecting to understand the full picture.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":710,"cache_read_input_tokens":28799,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":710},"output_tokens":12,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"278bf40c-f1a9-45b2-b220-2c3360021a52","uuid":"45483b7d-2430-4f29-bc98-8ab290fda51c","request_id":"req_011Cccy5xBqfPX4NVmmEmXf7"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01XCNraveesKuyJjcr2waQrk","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I can see the issues clearly:\n\n- `/app`: `app-user` has empty configure (broken), and `ops-user` has full access (wrong)\n- `/ops`: `ops-user` has no permissions at all (missing)\n\nLet me fix all three issues:"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":710,"cache_read_input_tokens":28799,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":710},"output_tokens":12,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"278bf40c-f1a9-45b2-b220-2c3360021a52","uuid":"fa320641-1028-4451-9e2b-4c37eba0d6f2","request_id":"req_011Cccy5xBqfPX4NVmmEmXf7"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01XCNraveesKuyJjcr2waQrk","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01GcVkV8mjEpiRTGn3J41D8F","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"NS=karma-rabbitmq-amqp-block-upgrade-01-8323c0a5-cluster-a\n\n# 1. Remove ops-user's permissions on /app (wrong vhost access)\nkubectl -n $NS exec rabbitmq-0 -- rabbitmqctl clear_permissions -p /app ops-user\necho \"Cleared ops-user from /app\"\n\n# 2. Fix app-user's configure permission on /app (was empty, needs .*)\nkubectl -n $NS exec rabbitmq-0 -- rabbitmqctl set_permissions -p /app app-user \".*\" \".*\" \".*\"\necho \"Set app-user full permissions on /app\"\n\n# 3. Grant ops-user full permissions on /ops (was missing entirely)\nkubectl -n $NS exec rabbitmq-0 -- rabbitmqctl set_permissions -p /ops ops-user \".*\" \".*\" \".*\"\necho \"Set ops-user full permissions on /ops\"","description":"Fix RabbitMQ permissions: remove ops-user from /app, fix app-user configure on /app, grant ops-user access to /ops"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":710,"cache_read_input_tokens":28799,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":710},"output_tokens":12,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"278bf40c-f1a9-45b2-b220-2c3360021a52","uuid":"6fa48ae7-f06b-4621-9485-a9dded04e160","request_id":"req_011Cccy5xBqfPX4NVmmEmXf7"}
